Package VendingModel.VendingMachineClasses

Class SpecialVendingMachine

java.lang.Object
VendingModel.VendingMachineClasses.SpecialVendingMachine
public class SpecialVendingMachine extends Object
This is the SpecialVendingMachine class. It is a subclass of the VendingMachine class and it inherits the methods of the InterfaceVendingMachine. It has additional attributes from the superclass which are an ArrayList of ItemsSlots for the user, and a counter attribute for the transactions made in a single sale, Here, not only is the buying of items is done. but the creation of a product as well.
